{"tid":1531574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9月14 (六) 世界急救日 World First Aid Day，係咪應該搞返個以First Aid為主題嘅集會","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T02:51:24.000Z","uid":44916,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2cdbf8e2333455fa09e1e64a2b76a1ac768c4594","tid":1531574,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:14:14.000Z","msg":"＊當天好似已經有個中學生螢火之荊集會<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n影片區：<br />\n<br />\n「沙田反送中」警察阻止為示威者急救年輕的急救員因此痛哭失聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p2QjI9XAotc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dp2QjI9XAotc&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=5da6932a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p2QjI9XAotc</a><br />\n<br />\n8.31油麻地站：急救員痛哭<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DK3kDuXdFns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDK3kDuXdFns&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=63cdeb9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DK3kDuXdFns</a><br />\n港急救員831對警痛哭喊話 讓我進去救人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=500562320756677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D500562320756677&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=94c2d84d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=500562320756677</a><br />\n<br />\n621反送中示威遊行 | 無懼催淚彈 絕不拒醫的急救義工 【最強的救援後盾】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YhjYbqs1aCY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYhjYbqs1aCY&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=88b3f879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YhjYbqs1aCY</a><br />\n<br />\n【專訪】還是中學生的前線急救員「因愛香港」所以去救人「為香港出盡每一分力」。「眼被打爛女士的那天....我在場，不可能不是警察打的....」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MhfeYztMz7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMhfeYztMz7s&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=25502506\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MhfeYztMz7s</a><br />\n<br />\n【專訪】示威現場前線自願救護人員自發一起工作，威仔（化名）說：「...受傷最嚴重的，是那次在荃灣，晚上黑衣人被一些白衣人打，還有那位女士眼睛被打，那天是在尖沙嘴......」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xzYrmWLiWsg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxzYrmWLiWsg&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=5efee352\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xzYrmWLiWsg</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n文章區：<br />\n<br />\n【周日人物】功課未做完 槍彈已捱過 14、15歲的急救員：仗未完 還有校園<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/32kE9rK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32kE9rK&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=dadbe7be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32kE9rK</a><br />\n<br />\n【逃犯條例】憂太子站後腦受傷者失血過多 急救員：8・31衰過7・21<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2jWE115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jWE115&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=fc8b7bb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2jWE115</a><br />\n<br />\n【反送中】民間自組急救站日夜輪更守護 護士義工心酸：為何示威傷者不敢到醫院求醫<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2lHcP6P\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lHcP6P&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=c7d05195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2lHcP6P</a><br />\n<br />\n【香港白頭盔〡勇武FIRST AID】預了受傷被捕 90後女教師：我願意為他們擋<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2lortQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lortQk&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=1e530ced\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2lortQk</a><br />\n<br />\n【沙田遊行】急救員分勇武、執人、補位三梯隊 救援戰術大解構<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2lof9PS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lof9PS&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=fbb98648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2lof9PS</a><br />\n<br />\n【沙田遊行】人道中立社運急救員 搶救暈倒CID 防暴警曾阻接近<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kcnYMO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kcnYMO&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=5f07603c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kcnYMO</a><br />\n<br />\n【機場集會】救援受阻 急救員嘆內鬼陰霾籠罩示威：救誰都有風險<br />\n<a href=\"https://bitly.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitly.com%2F&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=22ad5f75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bitly.com/</a>"},{"pid":"fc3b5c91b74b65024e7b670e6d24cef8323ac4ba","tid":1531574,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"b99b9c507f573d62c526ba1d6672d4efee0e842f","tid":1531574,"uid":256632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"【持續更新】香港人九月日程表<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kEaguAX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kEaguAX</a>"},{"pid":"2415d9d85b9c129a0269a3c21694dcb682d49ab5","tid":1531574,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:15:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n請fa分享下"},{"pid":"01bb7e1d19ff293e33be6525b9c568c687bfa767","tid":1531574,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:15:58.000Z","msg":"都得啊 講埋人道災難<br />\n同埋班狗阻撚住救援<br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25acd5dd8d20b522308c326df343f528f7b215d2","tid":1531574,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c4c8a3be153a0818b85f5eab98af7af0764c91","tid":1531574,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da49a078636c5cb8ce286dc19d1b61ea767cda78","tid":1531574,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59aeafd1271450e89826dafb6ec2694c807ee0e5","tid":1531574,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:17:54.000Z","msg":"多謝first aid集會？"},{"pid":"d2e92cdbfe5b88293b9705ef008d8340314a13cb","tid":1531574,"uid":98731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:18:04.000Z","msg":"【美國巴絲】請聯絡你嘅地區同州嘅國會代表／議員<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dNDHwS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dNDHwS</a>"},{"pid":"45b82301c83e80d1c7b9368cd05947867a1599a2","tid":1531574,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d349b1c03e1f76a50670bb2f649e47702f2eff","tid":1531574,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723589cc93d47e10c00a43023b9b47509d37a71d","tid":1531574,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59aeafd1271450e89826dafb6ec2694c807ee0e5","tid":1531574,"uid":33984,